1.android 3.0提出

2.Activity可以有多個fragment

3.一個Fragment也可以被多個Activity重用

4.Fragment有自己的Lifecycle :onAttached -> onCreate -> onCreateView -> (onViewCreated) -> onActivtyCreate -> onStart -> onResume
                            -> Fragment is active -> onPause -> onStop -> onDestroyView -> onDestroy ->onDetach
                            -> Fragment is destroyed

5.模組化、可重用、適應性
